/android/app/release

# Firebase
.firebase
*.env

# NOTE: firebase_options.dart and android/app/google-services.json are committed
# on purpose. They hold only public Firebase client identifiers (apiKey/appId),
# which already ship in the web bundle and APK; access is gated by Firestore
# rules / App Check, not by hiding these. CI needs them to build.
# Real secrets (release keystore, key.properties, service account JSON) stay out
# of git and are injected in CI via GitHub Actions secrets.
